# StringProc files are executable Ruby that runs inside every player's Lich
# session - changes to them require review by the StringProc maintainer team.
# Enforcement needs branch protection on main with "Require review from Code
# Owners" enabled.
#
# Note: in-game submissions carry NEW procs inline inside room.json (they are
# externalized to .rb files post-merge), so this rule alone does not gate
# them - the Submission Normalize workflow labels such PRs `stringprocs` and
# they are excluded from data-only auto-merge.
gs/**/*.rb @elanthia-online/stringproc-reviewers
